data.comment: The match has started at Nabizao.
Throw-in for Paranaense in the half of Bragantino.
In the minute 1, Throw-in Paranaense.
Bragantino are too eager and fall into an offside trap.
Throw-in for Bragantino in their own half.
In the minute 4, Bragantino awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Throw-in for Paranaense at Nabizao.
A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
In the minute 5, Paranaense needs to be cautious. Bragantino have an attacking throw-in.
Braulio da Silva Machado awards the away team a throw-in.
Paranaense have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
In the minute 9, Corner awarded to Bragantino.
Paranaense have a goal kick.
Free kick for Bragantino in their own half.
In the minute 10, Paranaense push upfield but Braulio da Silva Machado quickly pulls them for offside.
Ball safe as Paranaense is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Braulio da Silva Machado awards Bragantino a goal kick.
In the minute 12, Ball safe as Paranaense is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Paranaense in their own half.
Throw-in Paranaense.
In the minute 14, Goal kick for Paranaense at Nabizao.
In Braganca Paulista, Bruno Tubarao (Bragantino) misses the target with a header.
In the minute 15, Free kick Paranaense.
Ligger (Bragantino) gets a yellow card.
Paranaense's Maycon Nikao breaks free at Nabizao. But the strike goes wide of the post.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Braganca Paulista.
In the minute 17, Can Bragantino capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Paranaense's half?
Ball goes out of play for a Paranaense goal kick.
Paranaense are in shooting range from this free kick.
In the minute 20, Paranaense drive upfield and Leo Cittadini gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Bragantino defender.
Corner awarded to Paranaense.
Bragantino to take a throw-in in Paranaense territory.
In the minute 21, Can Bragantino get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Paranaense's half?
Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
Paranaense awarded a free kick in their own half.
In the minute 24, Braulio da Silva Machado signals a Bragantino throw-in in Paranaense's half.
In Braganca Paulista a free kick has been awarded the home team.
Ball goes out of play for a Paranaense goal kick.
In the minute 25, Free kick for Bragantino in their own half.
Throw-in for Paranaense in their own half.
Goal! Paranaense have got their heads in front thanks to a Renato Kayzer strike.
In the minute 26, Thiago Heleno with an assist there.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Paranaense in their own half.
Bragantino awarded a throw-in in their own half.
In the minute 35, A throw-in for the home team on the opposite half.
Throw-in for Bragantino close to the penalty box.
Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
In the minute 37, Bragantino's Claudinho misses with an attempt on goal.
Braulio da Silva Machado awards Paranaense a goal kick.
Braulio da Silva Machado awards the home team a throw-in.
In the minute 39, Paranaense awarded a free kick in their own half.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Bragantino.
Paranaense's Ze Ivaldo has been booked in Braganca Paulista.
In the minute 41, Bragantino's Artur gets his shot away but it misses the target.
Paranaense have a goal kick.
Throw-in for Bragantino at Nabizao.
In the minute 42, Corner awarded to Bragantino.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Braganca Paulista.
Throw-in for Bragantino at Nabizao.
In the minute 44, Corner awarded to Bragantino.
Free kick for Paranaense in the half of Bragantino.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a throw-in for Bragantino, close to Paranaense's area.
In the minute 45, In Braganca Paulista Bragantino attack through Raul. The finish is off target, however.
Goal kick for Paranaense at Nabizao.
Braulio da Silva Machado will wait an extra 5 minutes before blowing the whistle to end the 1st half.
In the minute 45, Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Bragantino in their own half.
Free kick Bragantino.
Bragantino have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 45, Ball safe as Bragantino is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
Ytalo (Bragantino) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
In the minute 45, Paranaense have a goal kick.
The first-half has come to a close in Braganca Paulista.
The second half has started at Nabizao.
In the minute 47, Corner awarded to Bragantino.
Braulio da Silva Machado awards Paranaense a goal kick.
Goal kick for Bragantino at Nabizao.
In the minute 49, Bragantino advance rapidly upfield but Braulio da Silva Machado blows for offside.
Throw-in for Bragantino in their own half.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a Bragantino throw-in in Paranaense's half.
In the minute 51, Bragantino are caught offside.
Important block from the Paranaense defence as Ytalo fires in a strike for Bragantino.
Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
In the minute 52, Ball goes out of play for a Paranaense goal kick.
Free kick for Bragantino in their own half.
Christian for Paranaense has been booked by Braulio da Silva Machado and receives a first yellow card.
In the minute 54, It's a goal kick for the home team in Braganca Paulista.
Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
It's a goal kick for the away team in Braganca Paulista.
In the minute 57, Matheus Jesus is replacing Eric Ramires for Bragantino at Nabizao.
Mauricio Barbieri is making the team's second substitution at Nabizao with Alerrandro replacing Ytalo.
Throw-in Paranaense.
In the minute 60, Bragantino are whistled for offside.
Can Paranaense get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Bragantino's half?
Throw-in for Paranaense in the half of Bragantino.
In the minute 62, Paranaense awarded a free kick in their own half.
Braulio da Silva Machado waits before resuming play because Khellven for Paranaense is still down.
Braulio da Silva Machado awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 64, Free kick for Bragantino in their own half.
Paranaense drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
Corner awarded to Bragantino.
In the minute 65, In Braganca Paulista Bragantino drive forward through Artur. His shot is on target but it's saved.
Bragantino drives forward and Claudinho gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
Throw-in high up the field for Bragantino in Braganca Paulista.
In the minute 67, Khellven is back on the pitch.
Morato (Bragantino) is first to the ball but his header is off-target.
In the minute 68, Paranaense have a goal kick.
Paulo Autuori (Paranaense) is making a first change, with Jaime Alvarado replacing the possibly injured Khellven.
Bragantino make their third substitution with Morato replacing Bruno Tubarao.
Jaime Alvarado is booked for the away team.
In the minute 71, Corner awarded to Bragantino.
Bragantino awarded a free kick in their own half.
Paranaense needs to be cautious. Bragantino have an attacking throw-in.
Lucas Halter is on a sub for Christian for Paranaense.
In the minute 72, The away team have replaced Carlos Eduardo with Reinaldo. This is the third substitution made today by Paulo Autuori.
In the minute 73, Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Bragantino.
At Nabizao, Richard has been yellow-carded for the away team.
Claudinho for Bragantino drives towards goal at Nabizao. But the finish is unsuccessful.
Mauricio Barbieri (Bragantino) is making a fourth substitution, with Thonny Anderson replacing Artur.
In the minute 79, Free kick for Bragantino in the half of Paranaense.
In Braganca Paulista a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Raul (Bragantino) has received a yellow card from Braulio da Silva Machado.
In the minute 81, Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
Free kick for Paranaense in the half of Bragantino.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a throw-in for Paranaense, close to Bragantino's area.
In the minute 83, Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Bragantino in their own half.
Paranaense drive forward at breakneck speed but are pulled up for offside.
Walter is replacing Renato Kayzer for Paranaense at Nabizao.
In the minute 86, Jan Hurtado is replacing Edimar for the home team.
The away team have replaced Richard with Lucho Gonzalez. This is the fifth substitution made today by Paulo Autuori.
Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
In the minute 87, Corner awarded to Bragantino.
Bragantino have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
Claudinho of Bragantino gets in a strike, but is off target.
In the minute 88, Goal kick for Paranaense at Nabizao.
Bragantino awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Bragantino in their own half.
Jan Hurtado gets his shot on target but fails to score for Bragantino.
Bragantino awarded a free kick in their own half.
Corner awarded to Bragantino.
Free kick for Paranaense in their own half.
The 2nd half is prolonged by 8 minutes of added time.
Corner awarded to Paranaense.
Paranaense have been awarded a corner by Braulio da Silva Machado.
Free kick for Bragantino in their own half.
Bragantino have a dangerous throw-in.
Bragantino awarded a free kick in their own half.
Throw-in for Bragantino close to the penalty box.
Braulio da Silva Machado awards the home team a throw-in.
Corner awarded to Bragantino.
Ball goes out of play for a Paranaense goal kick.
Braulio da Silva Machado signals a free kick to Bragantino in their own half.
The match is over. Final score 0-1.
Walter (Paranaense) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
